item.title: CVE-2020-11084|2024-08-04T11:21:14.654Z -- yabobjonez -- ipear
item.description: In iPear, the manual execution of the eval() function can lead to command injection. Only PCs where commands are manually executed via "For Developers" are affected. This function allows executing any PHP code within iPear which may change, damage, or steal data (files) from the PC.
